                      ],
                      "text": "的同時，也可以提高琴的元素戰技造成的傷害。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 47,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Albedo_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "阿貝多",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器的特效對阿貝多的元素戰技傷害提高較多（雖然提升幅度低於武器【辰砂之紡錘】），且提供的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "可加強阿貝多元素爆發的釋放頻率。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 26,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Bennett_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "班尼特",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "班尼特的輔助能力可以被該武器副詞綴提供的充能與不錯的基礎攻擊力極大地提高，也能增加少量的元素戰技傷害，十分推薦給班尼特使用。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 39,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Xingqiu_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "行秋",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "該武器可以有效提高元素戰技傷害和",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "元素充能效率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，以此提高行秋的輸出能力。",
                      "type": "text"
